      ],
      "direct_rvv_policy": "vlse32.v/vsse32.v for element-strided i32 reads and writes; vluxei32.v/vsuxei32.v with i32 element indices shifted to byte offsets for indexed reads and writes; masked non-unit memory forms use the same address policy with v0.t and false-lane preservation"
